reviewText: I have a feeling that the editorial review is a slight bit of a mishap - Unless this is "Backyardigans rage like you never seen them before"!!!!

2  Disc  Set,  Disc  One  (  Road  Rage IV  DVD )  Disc  Two  ( Road  Rage  IV  Audio  CD  Soundtrack ).  The  Soundtrack  has  (1)  Molested  Hombre,  Oddman,  Hit  by  a  semi,  Hudson  Drags,  The  last  Mile  Ox  Vs.  Thumderbird,  ELB  Featuring  Joe  D.B.  THIS  IS  A  GREAT  BUY !!!!!!
